---
import BaseHead from '../../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import { brand } from '../../../config/brand';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="de">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Services - Revenue Systeme | UHL Systems" description="Von der Diagnose bis zur kompletten Umsetzung. Revenue Leak Audit, Revenue Systems Consulting und laufender System-Support - waehle dein Level." />
		<style>
			.section-heading {
				font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
				line-height: 1.1;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
			}
			.hero-headline {
				font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px);
				line-height: 1.1;
				letter-spacing: -0.03em;
			}
			.cta-primary {
				background-color: var(--color-accent);
				color: var(--color-bg);
				border-radius: 999px;
				padding: 14px 36px;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: all 0.2s;
			}
			.cta-primary:hover {
				box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.35);
				color: var(--color-bg);
			}
			.cta-ghost {
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				border-radius: 999px;
				padding: 14px 36px;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				transition: all 0.2s;
			}
			.cta-ghost:hover {
				border-color: var(--color-accent);
				color: var(--color-text);
			}
			.service-card {
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				background: var(--color-bg2);
				border-radius: 16px;
				padding: 48px 40px;
				transition: all 0.3s;
			}
			.service-card:hover {
				border-color: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.25);
				background: var(--color-bg3);
			}
			.content-width {
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<!-- Hero -->
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-24 md:py-36">
			<div class="content-width text-center">
				<p class="fade-in mb-6 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Services</p>
				<h1 class="hero-headline fade-in fade-in-delay-1 font-display font-bold text-text">
					Repariere das System, nicht die Symptome
				</h1>
				<p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
					Ob du erstmal eine Diagnose brauchst, ein strategisches Playbook oder ein komplett aufgebautes Revenue System - wir passen den Umfang an das an, wo du gerade stehst.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
			<div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -z-10 h-[800px] w-[800px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,255,136,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
		</section>

		<!-- Service Cards -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-28">
			<div class="content-width">
				<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">

					<!-- Revenue Leak Audit -->
					<div class="service-card flex flex-col">
						<div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
							<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Revenue Leak Audit</h2>
								<p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark uppercase">Diagnose</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="mb-6 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Komplette Diagnose deines Revenue Systems. Wir analysieren jede Phase von Traffic bis LTV, identifizieren jedes Leck und liefern eine priorisierte Roadmap zur Behebung.
						</p>
						<div class="mb-6 border-t border-border pt-6">
							<span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-text">€1k - €2k</span>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-dark">Einmalige Investition</p>
						</div>
						<div class="mt-auto space-y-3">
							<a href="/de/services/audit" class="cta-primary block w-full text-center">
								Mehr erfahren
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Die Methode - highlighted -->
					<div class="relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-accent/40 bg-bg2 p-10 shadow-[0_0_48px_rgba(0,255,136,0.06)] transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/60">
						<div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-accent px-5 py-1 font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-bg">BELIEBTESTE WAHL</div>
						<div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
							<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.375 2.625a1 1 0 0 1 3 3l-9.013 9.014a2 2 0 0 1-.853.505l-2.873.84a.5.5 0 0 1-.62-.62l.84-2.873a2 2 0 0 1 .506-.852z"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Die Methode</h2>
								<p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark uppercase">3-Monats-Engagement</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="mb-6 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Alles aus dem Audit, plus 3 Monate intensive Zusammenarbeit. Wir designen deine komplette Revenue-Architektur und bauen das Execution Playbook.
						</p>
						<div class="mb-6 border-t border-border pt-6">
							<span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-text">€3k - €6k</span>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-dark">3-Monats-Engagement</p>
						</div>
						<div class="mt-auto space-y-3">
							<a href="/de/services/consulting" class="cta-primary block w-full text-center">
								Mehr erfahren
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Revenue Systems Consulting -->
					<div class="service-card flex flex-col">
						<div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
							<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18"/><path d="M9 21V9"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Revenue Systems Consulting</h2>
								<p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark uppercase">Strategie + Umsetzung</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="mb-6 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Dein dediziertes Revenue-Systems-Team. Wir bauen alles - Dashboards, Funnels, Automations - und loesen Probleme direkt. Kein Scope Limit.
						</p>
						<div class="mb-6 border-t border-border pt-6">
							<span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-text">€5k - €20k</span>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-dark">Laufendes Engagement</p>
						</div>
						<div class="mt-auto space-y-3">
							<a href="/de/services/consulting-process/" class="cta-primary block w-full text-center">
								Mehr erfahren
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- The UHL Method -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-28">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Die Methode</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					U &ndash; H &ndash; L
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-20 max-w-xl text-center text-muted">
					Unlock Hidden Leverage. Drei Phasen. Ein System. Kompoundierende Ergebnisse.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
					<!-- U -->
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-accent font-display">U</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-text">Uncover Revenue Leaks</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Tiefgreifendes Audit deines aktuellen Systems. Wir analysieren jeden Touchpoint ueber alle 7 Stationen, identifizieren jedes Leck und quantifizieren den Umsatz, der auf der Strecke bleibt.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- H -->
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-accent font-display">H</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-text">Hack Conversion Systems</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Datengetriebenes Strategie-Design mit bewaehrten Frameworks. Wir bauen deine Revenue-Architektur mit klaren Prioritaeten, Timelines und erwartetem Impact pro Hebel.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- L -->
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-accent font-display">L</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-text">Leverage Existing Traffic</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Systematische Umsetzung fuer maximalen ROI. Wir bauen, testen und optimieren jede Komponente deines Revenue Systems, bis es kompoundiert - ohne zusaetzliche Werbeausgaben.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-28">
			<div class="content-width text-center">
				<p class="mb-4 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Nicht sicher, wo du anfangen sollst?</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 font-display font-bold text-text">
					Buche einen 30-Minuten Strategy Call (€97)
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-14 max-w-xl text-muted">
					Wir gehen gemeinsam deine Revenue-Pipeline durch und empfehlen den richtigen Startpunkt. 30 Minuten.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
					<a href={brand.strategyCall.checkoutUrl} class="cta-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
						Strategy Call buchen - €97
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
					</a>
					<a href="/shop" class="cta-ghost inline-flex items-center gap-2">
						DIY-Tools ansehen
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
					</a>
					<p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-muted">30 Min | €97 | Zahlung bei Buchung</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
